text: "Coconut" is a 1972 song by Harry Nilsson and is the third single from his 1971 album Nilsson Schmilsson. It went to number 5 in Canada, number 8 in the United States and number 42 in the United Kingdom. It was covered by Dannii Minogue in 1998. == References == Category:1972 songs Category:Harry Nilsson songs Category:Dannii Minogue songs Category:Baha Men songs
